# Scope Memory Migrations

Place forward-only SQLite migration files in this directory when the scope-memory schema changes.

Rules:
- use zero-padded numeric prefixes such as `0002_add_scope_owner.sql`
- keep migrations idempotent where possible
- do not edit already-applied migration files
- update `schema.sql` so fresh projects still bootstrap correctly from scratch
- rerun `uv run python tools/init_scope_memory.py` after adding a migration
